                <div class="div-line"></div>

                <h3 class="subheading">Overview: EV Bikes vs Petrol Bikes — What's the Difference?</h3>
                <p>EV bikes run on rechargeable batteries and electric motors, providing <span class="font-weight-700">zero-emission rides</span> with quieter operation. Petrol bikes, on the other hand, use internal combustion engines powered by petrol to generate power and are known for their strong top-end performance.</p>
                <p>Both types have unique advantages and limitations. Let's compare them in detail.</p>

