                <p>Petrol bikes generally have a <span class="font-weight-700">well-established resale market.</span> EV bikes, being newer in India, have uncertain resale values, but this is expected to improve as their popularity increases.</p>
                <p>Battery health plays a big role in determining the resale value of EV bikes, whereas petrol bikes hold value based on age, mileage, and brand demand.</p>

